\f0\fs24 \cf4 <$Scr_Cs::4>
\f4\fs32 \\cm\{100\}
\f0\fs24 \cf0 <!$Scr_Cs::4>
\f1\fs32 ), and 
\f0\fs24 \cf4 <$Scr_Cs::4>
\f4\fs32 \\m\{1\}
\f0\fs24 \cf0 <!$Scr_Cs::4>
\f1\fs32  is a little more than 
\f0\fs24 \cf4 <$Scr_Cs::4>
\f4\fs32 \\inch\{39\}.
